        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-09 13:00:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nGot it, but I disagree and will not accept this change.  More generally, we're not accepting Sonar changes for 2 reasons : (a) they take an inordinate amount of the reviewers time and (b) the LF Sonar is not imposing coding standards that the PTLs have agreed to.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
